public class GraphFactoryImpl
extends Object

Implementation of a basic node and edge factory. If possible set Attributes to objets.

Return AbstractNode or AbstractEdge.

newEdge

public AbstractEdge newEdge(Node source,
                            Node target)
Description copied from interface: GraphFactory
Create a new edge. This method don't force the type of edge (directed or undirected). That means it is directed by default but will be considered as undirected if queried from an UndirectedGraph.

Edge's weight is 1.0 by default.

Specified by:
newEdge in interface GraphFactory
Parameters:
source - the edge's source
target - the edge's target
Returns:
a new proper edge instance
